# Use llama.cpp to load a Quantized LLM
llm = Llama(model_path="../openhermes-2.5-mistral-7b.Q4_K_M.gguf", n_gpu_layers=-1, n_ctx=9096, stop=["Q:", "\n"])
topic_label = btu.process_dataset(llm, df) # 480 minutes
